high_descs: Move to the large kitchen dining table by the statue
Pick up the white vase that is sitting on top of the table behind the laptop
Carry the vase to the large floor lamp to the right of the side table
anns.task_desc: Carry a vase while turning on a lamp

high_descs: Turn around and go straight back through the room. Turn right to face the desk.
Pick up the white vase on the edge of the desk.
Carry the vase and turn to the right and go straight. Then turn right in the next room to find the black table.
Holding the vase, turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Carry a vase to turn on the lamp.

high_descs: Turn around and walk straight to the end of the room then turn right and face the table
Pick up the white vase from the table
Turn right then walk straight in the living room and right again and face the table next to the piano
Hold the vase up to the lamp and turn on the light
anns.task_desc: Collect a vase to look at it under the lamp
